# .trivyignore — suppress findings that reflect intentional architecture decisions.
#
# Format: one AVD-* or CVE-* ID per line, optionally followed by an expiry date:
#   AVD-AWS-0017 exp:2027-01-01
#
# ── CloudWatch ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Flow log groups use AWS-managed encryption. CMK adds cost and operational
# overhead without meaningful security improvement for network telemetry.
AVD-AWS-0017

# ── VPC ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Default security group restrictions are enforced at the resource level.
# The default SG is tagged and managed via aws_default_security_group if needed.
AVD-AWS-0178
